<h2>How To Save 50%</h2>
<p style="text-align:left;">Since websites that add the web directory to their website contribute web traffic to the BungeeBones network for all our advertisers to benefit from, BungeeBones pays webmasters that host the web directory script 50% of whatever sales of paid links their site makes. 

<h2>By simply adding the BungeeBones script to your own website you can become your own first customer!</h2> Sign up for a paid position from your own web directory on your own website and you will instantly receive a 50% commission or rebate on your advertising costs. If you have already paid for your placement before adding the web directory just cancel it and then repurchase from your own directory installation to receive your rebate.

